	title : "How to write a great Letter of Continued Interest &#038; A Successful Example",		// 뉴스 제목
	
	thumbnail : {		
		excerpt : "<p>So, you’ve been waitlisted (or deferred) from a school you love. Go ahead and toss salt over your shoulder, light incense, and rub your hands together praying to get off the waitlist.  Or you could write a Letter of Continued Interest (LOCI)&#8211;your best shot at turning the tide. What is a LOCI? A LOCI (we [&hellip;]</p>",	// 섬네일에 보일 내용
		imageUrl : "https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/unnamed-1024x541.png"	// 섬네일 이미지 URL
