	title : "Point Avenue Updates: Royal Thai Ambassador&#8217;s visit to PA Cau Giay, Community Day &#038; Potluck Party",		// 뉴스 제목
	
	thumbnail : {		
		excerpt : "<p>Royal Thai Ambassador visited Point Avenue Cau Giay office Point Avenue is honored to welcome the Royal Thai Ambassador to our office! 👏 Our Point Avenue Thailand Leadership team had a fruitful discussion with Mr.Tanee Sangrat, Ambassador of Thailand to Vietnam, and Ms. Nareekarn Srichainak, Head of Protocol and International Cooperation Sections, on New Learning [&hellip;]</p>",	// 섬네일에 보일 내용
		imageUrl : "https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/community-day-PA-1.jpg"	// 섬네일 이미지 URL
	}
	
	date: "2020-07-28T14:56:37",
	lang : "en",		// 언어속성
	newsletter : {
		contents : "<p><strong>Royal Thai Ambassador visited Point Avenue Cau Giay office</strong></p> <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Point Avenue is honored to welcome the Royal Thai Ambassador to our office! </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">👏</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Our Point Avenue Thailand Leadership team had a fruitful discussion with Mr.Tanee Sangrat, Ambassador of Thailand to Vietnam, and Ms. Nareekarn Srichainak, Head of Protocol and International Cooperation Sections, on New Learning Approach and Education through Public-Private Partnership.</span></p> <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As Point Avenue is opening an office in Bangkok and on the way to become the premier education technology company in Southeast Asia, we are very glad to receive support from the Royal Thai Embassy, Hanoi for our character-based education. We pledge to commit to more activities hosted by the Embassy to promote education and the cordial relations between Vietnam and Thailand! </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">🇻🇳🇹🇭🤝</span></p> <p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2354" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Thai-Embassy-Point-Avenue-1.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="720" /></p> <p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2352" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Thai-Embassy-x-Point-Avenue-3.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="720" /></p> <p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2353" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Thai-Emb-x-Point-Avenue-2.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="720" /></p> <p><strong>Celebrated the success of Summer Camp Session 2 with Community Day &amp; Potluck</strong></p> <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The 2nd Session of Point Avenue Summer Camp had a grand finale with the Community Day event! For this event, Point Avenue Long Bien transformed into a multi-floor playground, where campers and parents engaged in many entertaining activities such as decorating cookies, drawing animals, face-painting or taking funny photos 🍪🎨📸 We also put the students newly-gained knowledge and skills to the test with trivia competitions, workout challenges, and more! 🚨💪 Everyone had a wonderful time before enjoying a cozy Potluck lunch.</span></p> <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Congratulations to all campers for graduating, and we hope to see you again in the Fall semester! 👏</span></p> <p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2351" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/community-day-PA-1.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="640" /></p> <p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2349" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/community-day-3.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="640" /></p> <p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2350" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Community-Day-PA-2.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="640" /></p> <p><strong>Point Avenue students spent Saturday afternoon cleaning up Hanoi’s neighborhood</strong></p> <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Following the success of the Keep Hanoi Clean event last June where 143kg of garbage was collected, Point Avenue mentors &amp; students had another meaningful outing with Keep Hanoi Clean on Saturday, 25 July. </span></p> <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This time, we cleaned up the park and fields around Star Lake, near the Korean embassy. This is a beautiful area where many people come to relax but also burn their trash. As a result, lots of litter and half-burned objects are left behind. While picking up trash in the hot sun, we also had an opportunity to have conversations and bond outside of our PA offices. </span></p> <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We had a great time as sanitation warriors and we look forward to doing more good for our city! 👏</span></p> <p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2360" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/KHC-x-PA-4__0.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="960" /></p> <p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2359" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/KHC-x-PA-3__0.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="960" /></p> <p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2361" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Keep-Hanoi-Clean-x-PA-1_.jpg" alt="" width="1478" height="1108" /></p>",		// 뉴스레터 내용, 
	}
},
	
