	title : "Point Avenue Updates: AmCham Pool Party &#038; Summer Camp Session 2",		// 뉴스 제목
	
	thumbnail : {		
		excerpt : "<p>The first half of July has gone by with many interesting events. In particular, his July, both Point Avenue Cau Giay &amp; Long Bien campus are full of laughter and interesting experiences for students attending Summer Camp Session 2. Let&#8217;s take a look at what we have been doing at Point Avenue recently! Point Avenue [&hellip;]</p>",	// 섬네일에 보일 내용
