	date: "2020-07-21T09:32:03",
	lang : "en",		// 언어속성
	newsletter : {
		contents : "<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The first half of July has gone by with many interesting events. In particular, his July, both Point Avenue Cau Giay &amp; Long Bien campus are full of laughter and interesting experiences for students attending Summer Camp Session 2. Let&#8217;s take a look at what we have been doing at Point Avenue recently!</span></p> <p><b>Point Avenue Team brought colors to AmCham 4th of July event</b></p> <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">On July 4th, Point Avenue Team participated in the Fourth of July Pool Party and BBQ event, hosted by the American Chamber of Commerce Vietnam to celebrate America&#8217;s 244th birthday! Through the event, our team interacted with many parents and students, and our face-painting booth proved to be a big hit with the attendees.</span></p> <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Point Avenue would like to thank </span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/AmChamHanoi/?eid=ARCDKBf5aqo9tOZQXEDvhZoiyGuUz33W_i9MMscItzLdizsPcTwOnxTrwEjz-9S4AvwaN5x8lfhT8vGj&amp;fref=tag"><span style="font-weight: 400;">AmCham Hanoi</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> for organizing the event, which gave everyone a chance to mingle and cool off during the hot summer months! </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">🏖</span></p> <p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2312" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/point-avenue-amcham-1.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="640" /></p> <p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2311" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/point-avenue-amcham-2.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="667" /></p> <p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2310" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/point-avenue-amcham-3.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="640" /></p> <p><b>Point Avenue Summer Camp Session 2 is halfway through</b></p> <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Point Avenue&#8217;s Summer Camp session 2 program is half way through, and our students are getting excited every day! Elementary students continue to explore many new things on a variety of topics, from English writing skills in Contemporary Journalism class, to how to operate and control robots in the Coding &amp; Robotics class. Middle school and high school students also expand their understanding and skill set through a wide range of activities and group projects including Leadership, Philosophy, Entrepreneurship and Design Thinking! 💼</span></p> <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In addition to classroom activities, students also have the opportunity to train physically in the gym and playgrounds, while listening to our guest speakers sharing their experience and inspiring them with public speaking and leadership skills 💪🎤  Everyone is ready to complete this summer camp with flying colors!</span></p> <p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2309" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/point-avenue-summer-camp-1.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="640" /></p> <p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2308" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/point-avenue-summer-camp-2.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="640" /></p> <p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2307" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/point-avenue-summer-camp-3.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="640" /></p> <p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2306" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/point-avenue-summer-camp-4.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="640" /></p> <p>&nbsp;</p>",		// 뉴스레터 내용, 
	}
},
	
