		contents : "<p><span style="font-size: 21px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;">Congratulations to all students on graduating Point Avenue’s Summer Boot Camp Session 1! <span class="_5mfr"><span class="_6qdm">🎓</span></span> </span></strong></span></p> <p><span style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;">We&#8217;re so proud to see students giving their maximum effort in the 21K Graduation Run, with so many successfully accomplishing that feat! <span class="_5mfr"><span class="_6qdm">🏃🏻</span></span><span class="_5mfr"><span class="_6qdm">🏁</span></span> Session 1 of the camp has come to an end, and we genuinely hope as mentors that our students will keep the healthy life habits that they have learned as well as the many friendships they have made at the camp. Click <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pg/PointAvenue/photos/?tab=album&amp;album_id=1302551249896110&amp;__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARDswNguJqwMgzNIpkkVbETIK8OPYa90YsBf6V4IGjEokjWLP919OuDYJ9BIGfyLaJsdYi-WXXEv2mtm4gtGqMDYs-0OH9GmZJHEKWCVv14KeQawua9Pp4Msg_M4RDPQKQRmEnNYd0YD3a9RcaCUJ73OafWC33uy1fOx8oP9zBfs5sT00zw6NilKZ7_X2M1K_hAxMMBc8i06YrcrE1dMrgMl1iIuuRuknrUSzopEr5OO2ZxqgPFQdREi3T3EeabULjsxxz4K4FjT6z6zBWoGyNfGq64-01ykZgTIFJ8_eBeyHD8wVGziRX2lWWv6xji_ygPqAK6vQ874GpZ5YsVH_UYJS0Xabw2Ykz8A3fmEWfteMpqstD58c9WjgiBb6jeJoR4_QlzsZrFxBk4hIOTcnsokwQudWQwEp8sKOcNlb41wCVBwOjn_22HN5kJjoZZ_v49AwpESLM5D-NOp16uXL2dQtQ&amp;__tn__=-UC-R">here</a> to see the full Summer Boot Camp 2019 &#8211; Session 1 Graduation Run &amp; Ceremony album. </span></p> <p><span style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;">See you all again in our 2019 Fall Regular Session that begins on August 20th!  <span class="_5mfr"><span class="_6qdm">🎉 </span></span></span><strong><span style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;">You can sign up for our Fall Session classes now via this <a href="https://www.surveymonkey.com/r/DWHVSCR">link</a>.</span></strong></p> <p><span style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;">Some moments from the graduation marathon and ceremony:</span></p> <p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1423" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/1.jpg" alt="" width="2048" height="1365" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1424" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2.jpg" alt="" width="2048" height="1365" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1425" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/3.jpg" alt="" width="2048" height="1365" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1426" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/4.jpg" alt="" width="2048" height="1365" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1427" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/5.jpg" alt="" width="2048" height="1365" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1428" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/6.jpg" alt="" width="2048" height="1365" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1429" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/7.jpg" alt="" width="2048" height="1365" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1430" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/8.jpg" alt="" width="2048" height="1365" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1431" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/9.jpg" alt="" width="2048" height="1365" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1432" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/10.jpg" alt="" width="1944" height="1296" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1433" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/11.jpg" alt="" width="2048" height="1365" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1434" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/12.jpg" alt="" width="2048" height="1365" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1435" src="https://www.pointavenue.com/wp-con