	thumbnail : {		
		excerpt : "<p>Dear Point Ave family, I don’t know how else I could start writing this other than by crying, because that’s how we started this journey. In the small TOONG office, I was scared of a gloomy future that required an overwhelming level of preparation. I also may or may not have gotten scared by a [&hellip;]</p>",	// 섬네일에 보일 내용
